The paper discusses the use of deep convolutional neural networks for image and video compression, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for signal processing and information theory, which could fall under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
